            <p><strong>Geometry Games</strong> are fast-paced platformers that combine rhythm-based gameplay with geometric obstacles. These games challenge your reflexes, timing, and pattern recognition skills. Whether you're a casual player or a hardcore gamer, geometry games offer endless entertainment and increasingly difficult challenges that will test your abilities.</p>
